data.description: Subject to short sale and third party approval. Please submit highest and best offers to listing agent by January 19th, 2024 before 2:00PM.  Assumable loan at 4.375%! Breathtaking all brick, energy efficient home is situated on 3.15 acres of waterfront property. 605 ft2 of stamped concrete rear porches have beautiful views of the Nansemond River. Appointed with high end finishes and details, this open floor plan provides natural light from foyer to kitchen, family rm, dining rm, full office; 1st floor ensuite for guests or generational room. Gourmet kitchen features quartz countertops, Viking cooktop, true walk-in pantry and access to rear porch; oversized den w/ gas fireplace, custom bookshelves, access to entertaining back porch! Includes expansive primary en-suite with huge walk-in closet, double-sink vanities and custom oversized shower. 2nd floor Media room has access to expansive balcony for those amazing sunset views. Saltwater pool. Permitted for dock, deep water access.
